00038 long int regFile::getRegNum(const char* regName) {
00039         if (RF.count(regName) > 0)
00040                 return RF.find(regName)->second;
00041         else if (atoi(regName) >= INIT_RENAME_REG_NUM) {
00042                 numRegs++;
00043                 return atoi(regName);
00044         }
00045         Assert(true == false && "getRegNum () must not have reached this point");
00046         return 0; //for compiler
00047 }

00049 long int regFile::getNumberOfRegs() {
00050         return numRegs;
